      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Need Fleet Financing?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">0% down payment. 100% full loan. No age limit. Fast approval for 10+ unit fleets. Preserve cash for operations.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
